  "stem": "<p>Which of the following functions has(have) a minimum value at &minus;4?</p><p>I. <i>f</i>(<i>x</i>) = &minus;8(2)<sup><i>x</i></sup> &minus; 4</p><p>II. <i>g</i>(<i>x</i>) = &minus;4(8)<sup><i>x</i></sup></p>",
