  "keys": ["d"],
  "rationale": "<p>Choice D is correct. For I: <i>f</i>(<i>x</i>) = &minus;8(2)<sup><i>x</i></sup> &minus; 4. As <i>x</i> &rarr; &infin;, the term &minus;8(2)<sup><i>x</i></sup> &rarr; &minus;&infin;, so <i>f</i> has no minimum. For II: <i>g</i>(<i>x</i>) = &minus;4(8)<sup><i>x</i></sup>. As <i>x</i> &rarr; &infin;, <i>g</i>(<i>x</i>) &rarr; &minus;&infin;, so <i>g</i> has no minimum either. Neither has a minimum at &minus;4.</p>",
